  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>これに懲りたら
二度と覗きなんて卑劣な真似はしないことだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Now that you've had to learn the hard way,
don't ever behave in such a despicable
manner as peeping.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>28</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>へ〜い</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yuuuup.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>21</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>はぁ、俺さま反省。
これくらいでこんなに痛い目にあわされちゃ
割に合わないし</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Haa. I'll do some self-reflecting. I don't wanna
suffer all that pain for something like this.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>11</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>反省が見られないわね。
なんなら縛りあげた状態で
女の子達に引き渡そうかしら</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'm not seeing any remorse. Maybe I should
tie you up and send you off to the girls.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>29</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>うっげェェェ！　それマジ勘弁！
タコ殴り確実じゃねェか！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Gahhhh! Seriously, forgive us!
We'd totally get our asses knocked around!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>21</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>わかった、もうしません！
もうしませんから〜！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I getcha, we won't do it!
We won't do it anymooore!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>11</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>そうか。　わかればいいんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I see. If you understand, that's good.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>28</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>やったわね、アスベル</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You did it, Asbel.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>29</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ああ。
俺は、女性を守れたんだな……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeah. I protected those women...!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
